    <div class="hero-unit">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            <h3>
            This web based application will be a central location for a
            moving company to manage Customers, Estimates, Jobs, Resources and
            any other information that managers may need to improve productivity. 
            This will be a one stop shop for providing informative statistics
            across company departments. Management can use this information to
            better prepare and plan future company business activities. You will be able to identify areas of success as well as
            areas that need improving. 
            </h3>
