 <div class="row-fluid">
     <div class="span3">
        <h3>Estimates</h3>
         <p>Schedule estimates. Complete "Over the phone" estimates.
         View and Modify estimate details.Provide dispatch with confirmed job
         schedule</p>
     </div> <!-- End Span 4 -->

     <div class="span3">
        <h3>Customers</h3>
         <p> View customer details and history.Understand 
         customer requirements. Classify customer type.
         </p>
     </div> <!-- End Span 4 -->

     <div class="span3">
        <h3>Dispatch</h3>
         <p> Schedule jobs based on information from sales department.
         Provide truck, crew, and material reqirements to dispatcher.  
         View job status and statistics. 
          </p>
     </div> <!-- End Span 4 -->

     <div class="span3">
        <h3>Storage</h3>
         <p> Provide storage usage and availability. Schedule incoming and
         outgoing storage jobs. Track storage accounts. Interact with existing
         billing syetem. 
         </p>
     </div> <!-- End Span 4 -->

 </div> <!-- /row-fluid -->
 <div class="row-fluid">

     <div class="span3">
        <h3>Equipment</h3>
         <p> 
         Track material and equipment usage. Plan material requirements based
         on job schedule. Track equipment suppliers and deliveries.Provide
         management and dispatch with necessary equipment information for planning
         upcoming jobs. 
          </p>
     </div> <!-- End Span 4 -->

     <div class="span3">
        <h3>Fleet</h3>
         <p> Record truck and vehicle information. Schedule vehicle
         maintenance. Create notifications for insurance and registration
         expiration. Provide truck capacities and availability to dispach
         system.
          </p>
     </div> <!-- End Span 4 -->

     <div class="span3">
        <h3>Admin</h3>
         <p>Provide accounting, sales, planning and job statistics. Central
         locaion for human resources.
         </p>
     </div> <!-- End Span 4 -->

